name: Asskey Punks 110
description:
Asskey Punks are a limited collection of 500 1/1 punk gifs. All 1/1, NON generative and handmade. Dropped 10 at a time.

Asskey Punks are not affiliated with Larva Labs at all, but rather pay tribute to the OG punks and the OG computer code. Updated with modern software and AI.

ASCII meets AI meets Photoshop. Glitched and stitched back together.

25% of ALL primary sales will go to local children's charities.
